			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="the drow commander and goblins arrive during the attack on the grove to find the player has already gone hostile to the tieflings by attacking them. The drow is amused that the player would start the slaughter without her and either joins them to finish off the tieflings, or gives futher orders if all are dead" />
